{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>As of now, Mechanica\u2019s development has been halted. For further updates are planned for the foreseeable future.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mechanica is a multiplayer open-world survival game involving building and programming. Create your own bases, defenses, manufacturing systems and more. Explore the map and expand the scope and complexity of your creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into an open-world, post-apocalyptic map as a sentient robot. Establish your first base and begin automating. You can invite up to 8 of your friends to join you over dedicated hosted servers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improve your defenses with a range of devices to keep the increasingly aggressive robots at bay. Use automation and creativity to remain alive in this hostile world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the visual programming system to make objects interact in any way you wish. Make a tripwire trigger a flamethrower, use a button to instantly lock down your base, control your mining outpost from across the map - anything is possible in Mechanica.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your own bases or fortify preexisting locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set up advanced defenses to fend off robots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Establish automated manufacturing systems to produce items for you</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the visual programming system to achieve advanced automation</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1226990/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738624081","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1226990/page.bg.jpg?t=17386